Decentrazlied file system 
This is a decentrazlied file system Demo made from the blockchain techonology. It is a web based application. 
It usese the IPFS system while recording metadata on Ethererum Blockchain.
The system store the CID making storage safe,decentralized and efficent. 
This project demonstrates the integration of modern Web3 technologies including React, Express.js, Solidity, Hardhat, MetaMask, Ethers.js, and IPFS.

......................................................................
Features
Upload files to IPFS
Store IPFS CIDs on the Ethereum blockchain
Connect with MetaMask
View uploaded file information
Rename uploaded files
Share files with other Ethereum addresses
Revoke file access
Secure ownership verification using wallet addresses
Event logging for blockchain transactions

